Just, wonderful, no words to express, the clearness, friendly talk, speedy solution, accomodating nature in fixing appointment, , absolutely wonderful  experience, of course, it costs, but worth..******** **** *********** **************************

I visited Dr. Vora to consult him on getting my wisdom teeth extracted. Everything, from the consultation to the actual extraction was incredibly smooth. Dr. Vora took the time to explain the condition of my teeth and the most ideal course of action. The entire extraction process took less than 10 minutes and I've felt no pain at all. I was allowed to get back to my daily routine the day after. 

If you're someone reading the reviews because you have dental issues and are nervous, trust me you're in great hands. Definitely recommend Dr. Vora to everyone.
I never knew about the dental scopey. He is the one, who made me understand about the measurement with the help of camera.
The possible solutions were very well explained to me...well enough to make a decision...the doctor was meticulously and simplied the explanation...

I visited Doc Sheel around Feb 2020 to get braces as my wedding was planned for year end. So I hardly had few months and everyone was unsure if it can be done in this short span. However I was assured by DrSheel that it can be planned and completed on or before time and there is no worry. He explained everything in detail and educated me about every little thing and what would best suit me which made me comfortable. Even though the lockdown was imposed right after my treatment started we could manage to complete the treatment well before time. All thanks to Dr Sheel I could smile laugh without any hesitation and look beautiful on my special day !

Regards,
Dr.Vora's Dental Care Centre
